                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 19,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Traveler_icon.png",
                      "name": "Traveler (Anemo)",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "An Anemo MC can hold the Elemental Skill Palm Vortex to unleash an Elemental Conversion and continuously unleash the Elemental Reaction Swirl. The Elemental Mastery sub-stats from this weapon can increase Swirl DMG. Additionally, the player must hold the Elemental Skill for more than 2 seconds to reach max Palm Vortex DMG. During this time, Slash DMG and Elemental DMG can increase this weapon's special effect to max stacks, which deals further Palm Vortex DMG.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 22,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Kaedehara Kazuha_icon.png",
                      "name": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Kazuha's talent Poetics of Fuubutsu increases the team's Elemental DMG according to Kazuha's base Elemental Mastery. This weapon greatly increases Kazuha's Elemental Mastery, thereby increasing the effect of Kazuha's talents. Since it is easy to acquire and has no refinement requirements, it's one of the most ideal choices for common players.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
